      "text": "A 45-year-old female with breast cancer is undergoing chemotherapy with cisplatin. Despite receiving antiemetics during the initial 24 hours, she experiences nausea and vomiting 48 hours after chemotherapy. Which of the following drugs below is most effective in preventing delayed emesis in this patient?",
      "options": [
